return sortConfig.direction === 'asc' ? -1 : 1; } if (aValue > bValue) { return sortConfig.direction === 'asc' ? 1 : -1; } return 0; }); } setFilteredOrders(filtered); setCurrentPage(1); }, [searchTerm, filterStatus, sortConfig, orders]); const handleSort = (key) => { let direction = 'asc'; if (sortConfig.key === key && sortConfig.direction === 'asc') { direction = 'desc'; } setSortConfig({ key, direction }); }; const getStatusBadge = (status) => { const statusConfig = { completed: { color: 'bg-green-100 text-green-800 border-green-200', icon: , text: 'Completed' }, pending: { color: 'bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 border-yellow-200', icon: , text: 'Pending' }, in_progress: { color: 'bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 border-blue-200', icon: , text: 'In Progress' },
